text: Tyrinthia nigroapicata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 2009. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Tyrinthia nigroapicata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2009
title: Tyrinthia nigroapicata
